data_table.description: Physical Activity Monitor (Actical®), Generation 3 Exam 2, New Offspring Spouse Exam 2, and Omni 2 Exam 2. The Actical physical activity monitor was administered at both the Offspring Exam 9 clinic exam (t_physactf_ex09_1b_0833s) and also at the Generation 3 Exam 2 clinic exam (t_physactf_ex02_3b_0914s). The Offspring Exam 9 study participants were instructed to take the monitor off during sleep, whereas the Generation 3 Exam 2 study participants were instructed to sleep with the monitor on. As a result, the two datasets may not be comparable for some measures. It is advisable to take this difference into account when analyzing the data.
